General.Name: Aspire Mining Ltd
General.Description: Aspire Mining Limited engages in the exploration and development of metallurgical coal assets in Mongolia. The company holds 100% interest in the Ovoot coking coal project that consists of one mining license located in north-western Mongolia. It also holds a 90% interest in the Nuurstei coking coal project that consists of one mining license, as well as engages in the pre-development, construction, and operation of the Erdenet to Ovoot railway in northern Mongolia. Aspire Mining Limited was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Ulaanbaatar, Mongolia.
